Brstarter
=========

Brstarter is a lightweight utility tailored for quickly setting up and running
command-line programs. Designed with flexibility in mind, it offers a
streamlined build system that allows you to get up and running in minimal time.
Brstarter is adaptable to different environments, including Windows and Linux,
with the potential to support other platforms as well.

The build system provides an easily customizable foundation, making it
straightforward to adapt Brstarter to new operating systems or environments as
needed. For guidance on adding support for additional platforms, see
platform-expansion.
